===Noun===
'''salmonella'''
{{wikipedia}}

#A common [[food-borne disease]] in humans. Symptoms include [[diarrhea]], fever and abdominal [[cramp]]s. 
#:''The mayonnaise left in the sun at the picnic caused everyone there to come down with '''salmonella'''.''
#A Genus of [[bacteria]], some species of which are responsible for certain diseases of [[food poisoning]].